                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8452" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0264</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2213 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">乘风、破浪、领航：中艺实业跨境发展的全球探索之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Soaring, Surfing, Leading：A Global Exploration Path for Cross-Border Development in Letright Industrial</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹聪，储诚相，张翊涵，苏庆，易诗琦，周金阳，吴梦潇，谢文杰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杭州中艺实业股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中艺实业；户外家居；跨境电商；数字化管理；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Letright industrial; Outdoor Home Furnishing; Cross-border E-commerce; Digital Management; Sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">后疫情时代，居家办公逐渐成为一种趋势。杭州中艺实业股份有限公司（以下简称“中艺实业”）借互联网和电子商务之东风，快速发展跨境电商，利用大数据和人工智能等资源辅助经营，B2C、B2B2C和D2C都在中艺实业跨境电商的发展中逐渐完善。但户外家具有其特殊性——这是一类季节性极强的产品，且对产品的设计有着更新的需求，也因此造就了户外家具市场的不确定性，这是中艺等类似户外家具企业面临的主要风险之一。那么如何尽可能地规避季节性对企业销售全过程的冲击，又如何以低成本推动企业跨境电商高效发展成了中艺实业面临的重大问题。中艺实业以完善企业各方面的管理为切入口，从生产销售再到自身组织架构进行进一步管理，融合互联网、大数据等新的技术优势，开辟企业的纵向一体化发展，并加快建设D2C。企业试图从管理中找到解决问题的突破口，以实现自身的可持续发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the era of post-epidemic, remote work has gradually become a trend. Leveraging the momentum of the internet and e-commerce, Letright Industrial Corp., LTD (hereinafter referred to as ‘LETRIGHT’) rapidly developed its cross-border e-commerce, utilizing big data and artificial intelligence resources to support its operations. The B2C, B2B2C, and D2C models have been progressively refined in the development of its cross-border e-commerce. However, outdoor furniture has its particularities—it is a highly seasonal product and requires continuous updates in design, which creates market uncertainties. This uncertainty is a significant risk faced by LETRIGHT and similar outdoor furniture companies. The major challenges for LETRIGHT have been how to mitigate the impact of seasonality on the entire sales process and how to promote efficient cross-border e-commerce development at a low cost. LETRIGHT has taken the improvement of comprehensive enterprise management as the entry point, further managing from production and sales to its organizational structure, integrating new technological advantages such as the internet and big data, opening up the vertical integration of the enterprise, and accelerating the construction of D2C. The company seeks to find breakthroughs in management to achieve sustainable development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《电子商务》、《跨境电商》、《企业战略》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">DTC营销模式；纵向一体化发展战略；绿色生产；6S管理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-07</td>
                            </tr>
